  <thing id="raSirSong" name="Songs of Sorrow" description="Your lamentations have a powerful effect on anyone who can hear them. You can cast the charm person spell once with this trait and regain the ability to do so when you finish a short rest. When you reach 3rd level, you can cast the enthrall spell once with this trait and regain the ability to do so when you finish a short rest. When you reach 5th level, you can cast\nthe hold person spell once with this trait and regain the ability to do so when you finish a short rest. Charisma is your spellcasting ability for these spells, and the targets of your spells must have the ability to hear you singing." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Cast Charm Person, Enthrall and Hold Person once per short rest.">
