  <thing id="raNymAu" name="Aurae Ancestry" description="You have Darkvision out to 60 ft., and you have advantage on Wisdom (Survival) checks when navigating by the stars. Starting at 3rd level, you can cast the faerie fire spell once with this trait and regain the ability to do so after a short or long rest. Starting at 7th level, you can cast the levitate spell once with this trait and regain the ability to do so after a short or long rest. Charisma is your spellcasting ability for these spells." compset="RaceSpec" summary="You have Darkvision out to 60 ft., advantage on Wisdom and can cast the faerie fire and levitate once per short rest.">
