  <thing id="OddFate" name="The Fates" description="Your otherworldy patron is actually a trio of ancient beings: the coven of hags known as the Fates. The Fates weave the destinies of all gods and mortals in their mag- ical loom, but whether they manipulate fate or merely record it is unknown. You have sworn yourself into the service of the Fates, and they sometimes reward you with glimpses into the future. However, you know that the Fates are utterly evil—whatever power that your pact affords you may pale in comparison to the ugly fate that they have likely prepared for you." compset="CustomSpec" summary="You have sworn yourself into the service of the Fates, and they sometimes reward you with glimpses into the future." uniqueness="unique">
